### MM Carver Framework Installation Procedure ###
# Rainer Poisel (rainer.poisel@fhstp.ac.at), 03062011

# Preamble

This installation procedure has been tested with Debian GNU/Linux only. But it
should also work with Ubuntu Linux and other .deb based distributions. 

# Packages

The following line has to be executed in order to meet the package requirements

$ aptitude install python cython python-magic ffmpeg libmediainfo-dev \
    sleuthkit build-essential

# Compilation

Compilation consists of compiling the C-Libraries and Python-Wrappers. Start
the procedure by invoking the following command:

$ make

